title: Ohio Wesleyan Announces November 2015 Public Events (Ohio Wesleyan University)
text: ( Source : Ohio Wesleyan University ) DELAWARE, OHIO - Ohio Wesleyan University today announced its November 2015 lineup of public events. For the latest OWU event information, including schedule changes, visit events.owu.edu. For Battling
